Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:14.93,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:15.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.83,0:00:18.91,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:23.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:26.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:30.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:34.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:36.84,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:40.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:45.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:48.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:51.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:54.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:59.54,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:03.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:11.34,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:15.13,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:19.01,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:24.88,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,200.389)}The Electric Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:24.88,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs235\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,690.389)}Kuragedall
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.88,0:01:29.50,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9\3c&H6A6661&\c&H000000&\fs60}Washigaki\NLighthouse
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Poochie! Poochie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.72,0:01:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Poochie! Poochie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.01,0:01:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking for your dog, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.21,0:01:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.75,0:01:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He ran that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Thanks so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Poochie! Poochie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.76,0:01:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Poochie! Poochie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.14,0:01:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Poochie?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.67,0:02:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it wasn't him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.46,0:02:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Poochie! Poochie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Poochie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Poochie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Poochie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Poochie! Poochie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.09,0:02:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Say... is that an alien?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It is an alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,An alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't pull so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone would be scared\Nafter seeing what I saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big emergency, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw an alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please. That's stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd seen a\Ndead body or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! You gotta hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you watch too many\NHollywood movies on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! I saw a dead body!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you change your story now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hurry already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.88,0:03:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It was right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an alien with a big head.\NIt looked like a jellyfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It attacked the guy like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.12,0:03:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that! It's a crime to\Ntease an officer of the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You adults never believe us kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I really did see it, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an alien with a huge head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no such things as aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll show you proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kota's such a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's forget him and go play!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody believes me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all the fuss about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,None of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're acting very strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really fall off a cliff?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hit your head? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.71,0:04:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, where's Big Brother's camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be furious with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:05:02.47,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9\3c&H6A6661&\c&H000000&\fs60}Washigaki\NLighthouse
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the one we've been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see soon enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Leave the child there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My electric shock will\Nput him out for an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:38.54,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Space-obsessed Kota\NKawamoto, ten years old,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:42.56,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,saw a jellyfish-like alien\Nnear Washigasaki Lighthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"Experts agree that it's an extremely\Nwell done trick photograph."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... a jellyfish alien, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.07,0:07:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, that's a pretty convincing fake\Nphoto that ten-year-old kid made.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's true that several\Nvillagers have gone missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.56,0:07:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but family circumstances are\Nbelieved to be the cause."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it might be Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, children these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you guys always have to pick on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Goro might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Shocker monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to speak to that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to see our Kota?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ask him about\Nthis morning's article.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, it's really\Nquite embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.15,0:08:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was hoping to\Nspeak to him directly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He came home yesterday in sort of a daze.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He's with a guest right\Nnow, as a matter of fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Another visitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They look just like Shocker combatants.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, Kota.\NIt's not nice to lie, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.59,0:08:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kota, would you show us to the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.30,0:08:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get you something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister! They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like Shocker's shown themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, look after Kota.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.01,0:09:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato will make you pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You've shown yourself, Shocker Cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, you will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You electric jellyfish monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.09,0:11:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Kuragedall!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, I will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider's body can withstand\N50,000 volts of electricity!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider... we shall meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:39.61,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I got separated in all the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If Kamen Rider hasn't shown\Nup, we might have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:14.50,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9\3c&H6A6661&\c&H000000&\fs60}Washigaki\NLighthouse
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, in Shocker's base\Nbeneath Washigasaki Lighthouse...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find humans who can\Nwithstand 5,000 volts
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and turn them into electro-people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,2,000 volts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.99,0:13:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,3,000 volts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,5,000 volts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.18,0:13:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He fails!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dispose of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who pass will be given\Nmassive electric charges,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,so that all who touch them will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:14:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use these electro-people to\Nkill Japan's political leaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And in time, we will kill all of humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring me the woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Proceed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Please, spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can lure out the\NKamen Rider and finish him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then no one can stand in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll dig out his heart myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, Kota!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Kota's mother was taken...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why they took his mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To lure out Hayato, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Several people in that village\Nhave already gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They're holding Kota's mother\Nat Washigasaki Lighthouse...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To take a child's mother...\NIt's unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems totally abandoned...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When Rider moves to save\Nher, trigger the dynamite!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider hasn't appeared yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing them, they must have\Nsome trick up their sleeve...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That fool Rider's run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it the second he gets\Nclose to the woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He's FBI scum. Just as good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.26,0:18:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.72,0:18:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... no matter the\Ndanger, I have to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.81,0:20:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.57,0:21:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.95,0:22:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of there, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.19,0:22:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Run to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.50,0:22:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.48,0:22:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.51,0:22:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.28,0:22:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.22,0:22:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.61,0:22:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kota!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.06,0:22:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.64,0:22:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.15,0:22:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.11,0:22:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kota, isn't that nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.64,0:22:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But where's Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.12,0:22:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.11,0:22:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.90,0:22:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.38,0:22:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.88,0:22:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you off doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.86,0:22:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.92,0:22:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:22:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wretched Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.85,0:23:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,next time we meet, I will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.80,0:23:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:24.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The persistent Colonel Zol\Nwill attack Japan again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.62,0:23:28.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And evil organization Shocker will\Ncontinue to create new cyborgs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.41,0:23:30.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in their efforts to conquer the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.86,0:23:33.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and disrupt our peace once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.90,0:23:36.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Keep fighting, our Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.12,0:23:40.66,Cont,,0,50,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.08,0:23:42.97,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.08,0:23:44.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.60,0:23:46.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is a blood-sucking trilobite.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:47.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker, in its quest to conquer the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.94,0:23:51.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,threatens the world-renowned\Ntrilobite scholar Doctor Shimura
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.22,0:23:53.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,into creating blood-sucking trilobites,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.15,0:23:55.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,which they intend to send\Nall around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.21,0:23:57.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.85,0:24:00.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "Reborn Fossil: The\NBlood-Sucking Trilobite!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.51,0:24:01.06,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs110\fscy90\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(567.167,720.389)}Reborn Fossil: \NThe Blood-Sucking Trilobite!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.25,0:24:11.09,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.68,0:24:13.68,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.68,0:24:15.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.64,0:24:18.68,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the villains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.18,0:24:21.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.06,0:24:22.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.94,0:24:24.73,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.73,0:24:26.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.52,0:24:28.57,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.61,0:24:34.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with all of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.28,0:24:37.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.87,0:24:41.54,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.96,0:24:45.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Electric Monster Kuragedall